            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指下跌-199.15點至9658.9478點，跌幅2.02%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日01:00，深證成指下跌199.15點（或2.02%），暫報9658.95點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.6%</li><li>近 1 月：-10.2%</li><li>近 3 月：-2.01%</li><li>近 6 月：-2.07%</li><li>今年以來：-5.34%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>青蒿素概念領跌-5.17%。其中    潤都股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002923:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002923\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002923-CN</a>)            下跌        10.01%            ;        德龍匯能(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000593:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000593\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000593-CN</a>)            下跌        3.43%            ;        新和成(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002001:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002001\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002001-CN</a>)            下跌        2.07%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>賽馬概念概念領跌-5.01%。其中    新華都(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002264:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002264\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002264-CN</a>)            下跌        6.35%            ;        羅牛山(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000735:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000735\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000735-CN</a>)            下跌        4.78%            ;        珠江鋼琴(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002678:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002678\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002678-CN</a>)            下跌        3.88%    。</p></section></main>",
